- `cloud_essd_entry`: ESSD Entry disk.

Default value: `cloud_efficiency`.', example='cloud_efficiency'),
    systemDiskEncryptAlgorithm?: string(name='system_disk_encrypt_algorithm', description='Encryption algorithm used by the system disk. Valid values: aes-256.', example='aes-256'),
    systemDiskEncrypted?: boolean(name='system_disk_encrypted', description='Whether to encrypt the system disk. Valid values:

